<HEADLINE>
<P>
A SURVIVOR REMEMBERS 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 It seems to me unreal that I live and watch the Oscars, where "Schindler's 
List" won as best picture.Tears run down my face. 
</P>
<P>
 In my mind's eye I can see my whole family in the gas chambers gasping for 
breath, among them my 12-year-old brother. I hear his screams, see his 
outstretched arms. But nobody helped the Jews then. 
</P>
<P>
 I survived to remember, and I say to you the skinheads are not a passing fad. 
They are real. I saw the German Hitler Youth. I was there when it started. 
</P>
<P>
 ROSE FUTTER 
</P>
<P>
 Los Angeles 
</P>
