<HEADLINE>
<P>
FRENCH AGENCY BOMBED 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
By Reuters 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 A bomb exploded outside a travel agency in the center of the French 
