 You won't get a box seat, but you might see a show for as little as $1. Sunday 
is your first shot at single tickets for that L.A. tradition, summer at the 
Hollywood Bowl. Visit the box office after 10 a.m. or call Ticketmaster for an 
evening of music, starry nights and, of course, fanciful picnics. 
</P>
