purchased with proceeds from fund-raising events she sponsored. She also sent 
Thanksgiving food baskets to needy families, staged holiday parties at the 
Veterans Hospital in Westwood and organized outings for needy children to 
movies, parks and other attractions. In Los Angeles on April 28 of a heart 
