<P>
 Werdegar nomination -- Because of an editing error, The Times on Friday 
incorrectly reported the educational background of California Supreme Court 
nominee Kathryn M. Werdegar. She graduated first in her class at George 
Washington University Law School. She also obtained a law degree from UC 
Berkeley's Boalt Hall. 
